{
  "fileData": "<?xml version="1.0"?>
<rdf:RDF xmlns="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#"
     xml:base="http://ont.enapso.com/truck"
     xmlns:v1="http://ont.enapso.com/truck/1.0.0#"
     xmlns:enh="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#"
     xmlns:owl="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#"
     xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#"
     xmlns:xml="http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace"
     xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#"
     xmlns:rdfs="http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#"
     xmlns:terms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/"
     xmlns:schema="https://schema.org/">
    <owl:Ontology rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck">
        <owl:versionIRI rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck/1.0.0"/>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">ENAPSO Haigo Transportation Ontology</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:Ontology>
    


    <!-- 
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    //
    // Object Properties
    //
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
     -->

    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#haCurrentLocation -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#haCurrentLocation">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Current Location</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasEndPoint -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasEndPoint">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has End Point</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasLoadingService -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasLoadingService">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Loading Service</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasMap -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasMap">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Map</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasOrder -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasOrder">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Order</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasOwner -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasOwner">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Owner</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasRate -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasRate">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Rate</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasRoutes -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasRoutes">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Routes</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasStartPoint -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasStartPoint">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Start Point</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasTruck -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasTruck">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Truck</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasUnLoadingService -->

    <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasUnLoadingService">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has Un Loading Service</rdfs:label>
    </owl:ObjectProperty>
    


    <!-- 
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    //
    // Data properties
    //
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
     -->

    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#DeliveryType -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#DeliveryType">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">delivery Type</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#address -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#address">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">address</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#averageFuelConsumption -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#averageFuelConsumption">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">average Fuel Consumption</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#averageSpeed -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#averageSpeed">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">average Speed</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#cargoVolume -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#cargoVolume">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">cargo Volume</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#chassisNumber -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#chassisNumber">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">chassis Number</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#costPerHour -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#costPerHour">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">cost Per Hour</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#costPerkm -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#costPerkm">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">cost Per km</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#deliveryAddress -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#deliveryAddress">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">delivery Address</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#deliveryDistance -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#deliveryDistance">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">delivery Distance</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#driveConfiguration -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#driveConfiguration">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">drive Configuration</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#expectedDeliveryDate -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#expectedDeliveryDate">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">expected Delivery Date</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#licenceNumber -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#licenceNumber">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">licence Number</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#loadCapacity -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#loadCapacity">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">load Capacity</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#loadingCost -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#loadingCost">
        <rdfs:label>loading Cost</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#loadingTime -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#loadingTime">
        <rdfs:label>loading Time</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#make -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#make">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">make</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#maximumSpeed -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#maximumSpeed">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">maximum Speed</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#mileageReadDate -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#mileageReadDate">
        <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#topDataProperty"/>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">mileage Read Date</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#model -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#model">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">model</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#name -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#name">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">name</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#noOfSeats -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#noOfSeats">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">no of seats</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#orderId -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#orderId">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">order Id</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#orderdate -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#orderdate">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">order Date</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#power -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#power">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">power</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#ratePerVolume -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#ratePerVolume">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">rate Per Volume</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#status -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#status">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">status</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#time -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#time">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">time</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#totalMileage -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#totalMileage">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">total Mileage</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#transportCharges -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#transportCharges">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">transport Charges</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#truckNumber -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#truckNumber">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">truck Number</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#unLoadingCost -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#unLoadingCost">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">un Loading Cost</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#unLoadingTime -->

    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#unLoadingTime">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">un Loading Time</rdfs:label>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- 
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
    //
    // Classes
    //
    ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
     -->

    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#DeliveryPlan -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#DeliveryPlan">
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasOrder"/>
                <owl:allValuesFrom rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Order"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasTruck"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onClass rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Truck"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#status"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Delivery plan means how a order deliver through which truck and using which route through map</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Delivery Plan</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#GeoLocation -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#GeoLocation">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Location"/>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Gro Location is a technique of identifying the geographical location of a person or device by means of digital information processed via the internet.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Geo Location</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Location -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Location">
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#address"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Location is a particular place or position.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Location</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Map -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Map">
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasRoutes"/>
                <owl:allValuesFrom rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Route"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Map</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Order -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Order">
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasRate"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onClass rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Rate"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasRoutes"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onClass rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Route"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#unLoadingTime"/>
                <owl:someValuesFrom rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#cargoVolume"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#deliveryAddress"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#expectedDeliveryDate"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#orderId"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#orderdate"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#status"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#transportCharges"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#loadingCost"/>
                <owl:maxQualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:maxQualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#loadingTime"/>
                <owl:maxQualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:maxQualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Order</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Rate -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Rate">
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasOwner"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onClass rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#TransportCompany"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#DeliveryType"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#ratePerVolume"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A rate calculator is the ratio between two related quantities in different units.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Rate</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Route -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Route">
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasEndPoint"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onClass rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Location"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#hasStartPoint"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onClass rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#Location"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>
            <owl:Restriction>
                <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ont.enapso.com/truck#deliveryDistance"/>
                <owl:qualifiedCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:qualifiedCardinality>
                <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer"/>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A transportation route is the regular path that is followed by a movement of people or goods.</rdfs:comment>
